name: Shiba Invasion CounterForce
description:
You are a Shiba Inu and very protective of your territory. Scare away cats and postmen to protect your home.

How to Play
  •  WASD or arrow keys to move
  • Space to bark

Bark at cats: 5 points

Bark at postman: 1 point

Postman reach your home: -3 points

Attribution

Music found on opengameart, by Juhani Junkala ("5 Action Chiptunes")
